{"tid":2391134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人質外交]踢爆大律師公會新主席夏博義反對特赦警暴受害人的真實原因","createTime":"2021-02-02T04:26:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T08:16:08.000Z","uid":26770,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"76b7a6151c4b807ad9335923bc184cc9014b20b1","tid":2391134,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:26:22.000Z","msg":"原討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2387994/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2387994/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n新主席夏博義話特赦不現實,但大家要問的係<ins>因何暴力示威不斷</ins>&hellip;<br />\n新屋嶺輪姦酷刑案涉事警員無任何後果, 荃灣警局輪姦案中法官濫用搜查令恐嚇到受害人流亡<br />\n<br />\n另外,夏博義指香港法官專業不受政治影響<br />\n<span class=\"red\">「赴湯杜火」案潘兆初法官話唔走就共犯, 但吳重儀/莫梓沖曾把街坊離開現場當身有屎的證據去判監</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大律師公會一再對司法迫害扮盲係由於怕認左各國會排除香港在法律合約之中的<em>高額金錢利益</em>,,呢點我一年前已寫文提過</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E6%86%82%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E5%8F%97%E6%90%8D-%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%B0%87%E4%BB%B2%E8%A3%81%E5%9C%B0%E9%BB%9E%E8%BD%89%E5%BE%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E7%AD%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%2586%2582%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2590%258D-%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%25BE%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E7%25AD%2589%2F&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BHljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=021c5d48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%2586%2582%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2590%258D-%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%25BE%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E7%25AD%2589%2F&h=3cc14c2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E6%86%82%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E5%8F%97%E6%90%8D-%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%B0%87%E4%BB%B2%E8%A3%81%E5%9C%B0%E9%BB%9E%E8%BD%89%E5%BE%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E7%AD%89/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"purple\"><span class=\"xx-large\">而更迫一切的係律政有份迫害政治異見者和警暴受害者的人其實係公會會員<br />\n夏博義係日後救自己人把政治犯當人質迫香港人接受兩邊特赦</span></span>"},{"pid":"76fdcc8a9ea8c10a0c0902ae2f0efa2d644a3bba","tid":2391134,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba52806c563404a686ea757af43103baa9df2e2f","tid":2391134,"uid":253016,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"不嬲香港堆法律撚都係扮盲<br />\n無視支共對香港入侵換高薪厚職"},{"pid":"06f5c4a548338345d43bc5c1203b78ccc5d4f764","tid":2391134,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ba52806c563404a686ea757af43103baa9df2e2f","tid":2391134,"uid":253016,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"不嬲香港堆法律撚都係扮盲<br />\n無視支共對香港入侵換高薪厚職"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"呢廿年一齊同支共做戲搵水"},{"pid":"0719af7f561cbc87a5b9f326d27bada57468b149","tid":2391134,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:31:16.000Z","msg":"Devils in the details<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">夏博義的發言係鋪路放生涉政治迫害的法律界人士..<br />\n利用偷換概念把受害人變人質迫香港人為救人接受不公義條件</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"brown\">行業組織睇的從來係行業利益而非是非對錯</span>"},{"pid":"3db558532c8e0fe6253278c3ea2e91aa4c4dc09f","tid":2